1
00:00:04,622 --> 00:00:05,822
​Why'd you do that?
为什么要那么说

2
00:00:08,400  --> 00:00:10,500
Why'd you take the blame?
为什么要去承担责任

3
00:00:12,244 --> 00:00:13,560
It's just easier.
为了大家方便

4
00:00:15,222 --> 00:00:17,022
She's more than willing to think
如果说是我闯的祸

5
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:19,722
that I'm the one that screwed it up.
她会更容易接受

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:27,000
We can't tell her we disobeyed a direct order.
总不能告诉她是我们违反命令吧

7
00:00:27,422 --> 00:00:28,488
You didn't.
你没有

8
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,866
I did.
违反命令的是我

9
00:00:31,800  --> 00:00:34,700
But I think you did the right thing.
但我觉得你是对的

10
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:36,044
You do?
是吗

11
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:38,380
Yes.
是的

12
00:00:39,766  --> 00:00:42,722
You're going to have to be careful.
你以后要多加小心

13
00:00:42,840  --> 00:00:44,320
What's that supposed to mean?
此话怎讲

14
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:46,800
It means you have feelings for Chloe.
你喜欢克洛伊

15
00:00:47,422 --> 00:00:49,720
And those feelings could get us into trouble.
这份感情可能会给我们带来麻烦

16
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:53,600
Don't let them cloud your judgment.
别让感情冲昏了头脑

17
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,644
Get some rest.
去休息吧